        modules:
        - weight: 90
          module: []
          statUsed: 0
          output: The Imperial Family accepts our offering and displays it within
            their private gardens. From this day forth, all who visit them shall
            bear witness to the magnificence of our fold.
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685506
          statUsed: 1
          output: 'At first, the Imperial Family was reluctant to show favor to any
            single sect, yet upon witnessing the grandeur of our sculpture, they
            chose to make an exception. They practically declared that we were doing
            them a service rather than the reverse!

            [Gained 2 Authority]'
